<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en"><head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, maximum-scale=1, user-scalable=no">
<title>新人红包</title>
<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="./Public/Home/css/bootstrap.min.css">
<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="./Public/Home/css/common.css">
<script src="./Public/Home/js/jquery-1.11.2.min.js"></script>
<script src="./Public/Home/js/flexible.js"></script>
<style type="text/css">
	#conten{
		background: #fedd46;
	}
	.box{
		padding: 15px;
	}
	.packs{
		border:solid 2px #3b211c;
		background: #fed42b;
		border-radius: 10px;
		padding: 10px;
		padding-bottom: 15px;
	}
	.packs .text-img{
		width:45%;
		margin: 15px auto;
		margin-top: 5px;
	}
	.packs-text-box{
		background: #fff;
		border-radius: 6px;
		padding-bottom: 15px;
	}
	.packs-text-box .link{
		width:80%;
		display: block;
		background: #fe7633;
		line-height: 3em;
		font-size: 16px;
		text-align: center;
		margin: 0 auto;
		border-radius: 99px;
		color: #fff;
		font-weight: bold;
	}
	.persnoal-box{
		display: -webkit-flex;
		padding: 15px;
	}
	.persnoal-box .avatar{
		width:48px;
		height: 48px;
		border-radius: 66px;
		margin-right: 15px;
	}
	.persnoal-box .text-p-img{
		width:5px;
		height: 10px;
		z-index: 9999;
		margin-top: 20px;
	}
	.persnoal-box .text-content{
		flex:1;
		background: #f3f3f3;
		border:1px solid #fed42b;
		margin-left: -1px;
		border-radius: 3px;
		padding: 10px;
		color: #3b211c;
		font-size: 14px;
		text-align: justify;
	}
	.text-content span{
		color: #ff2424
	}
	.liucheng{
		font-size: 16px;
		text-align: justify;
		line-height: 1.6em;
		margin-top: 15px;
	}
</style>
</head>

<body>

	
	<section id="conten">
		<img src="./Public/Home/img/invite-im.png">
		<div class="box">
			<div class="packs">
				<img class="text-img" src="./Public/Home/img/invite-text.png">
				<div class="packs-text-box">
					<div class="persnoal-box">
						<img class="avatar" src="./Public/Home/img/Avatar.png" id="imageurl">
						<img class="text-p-img" src="./Public/Home/img/persnoal-text-img.png">
						<p class="text-content">HI-我是<span id="nickname">社会主义接班人</span><br>我在聚点微淘送你2元新手红包，点击立即领取</p>
					</div>
					<a class="link" href="https://acbfbq.mlinks.cc/A0bS?openid={$openid}">立即领取</a>
				</div>
			</div>
			<p class="liucheng">
				领取流程：<br>1.点击立即领取，获得红包奖励<br>2.进入聚点微淘【APP-微信登录】<br>3.按照奖励规则领取对应福利
			</p>
		</div>
		
	</section>
	
	<footer>
	
	</footer>
</body>
<script>
$(function(){
	var openid = localStorage.getItem("openid");
	$.ajax({
		type:"post",
		url:"?s=Invite/getweixinuserinfo",
		data:{'openid':openid},
		dataType : "json",			
		success : function(data){
			if(data){
				$("#nickname").html(data[0]['nickname']);
				$("#imageurl").attr("src",data[0]['imageurl']);
			}
		}
	});
});
</script>

    
</html>